---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="About Julian Elliott" description="Learn more about Julian Elliott, data analytics enthusiast and automation tinkerer." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>👋 Hello, I'm Julian Elliott</h1>

      <p>
        I'm currently pursuing my <strong>MSc in Data Analytics</strong> at the University of Huddersfield, driven by a deep curiosity for turning both structured and unstructured data into meaningful, actionable insights. Whether it's optimising a process or illuminating a hidden trend, I thrive on the power of information used well.
      </p>

      <p>
        Beyond the classroom, I spend a lot of time in my personal <strong>homelab</strong>—my digital sandbox for learning, experimenting, and building. There, I dive deep into topics like virtualisation, containerisation, and automating just about anything that stands still long enough. My goal? A fully self-hosted ecosystem where learning never stops.
      </p>

      <h2>🔧 Tech I'm Exploring Right Now</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>🔁 Integrating <strong>n8n</strong> workflows into data pipelines</li>
        <li>🐳 Containerisation with <strong>Docker & Kubernetes</strong></li>
        <li>🖥️ Virtualisation via <strong>Proxmox</strong> and <strong>VMware</strong></li>
        <li>🌐 Network and firewall design for secure home infrastructure</li>
        <li>🏡 Creative <strong>IoT and home automation</strong> hacks</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>🌱 What's Got Me Curious</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>📊 <strong>Data Democratisation</strong> – bringing powerful insights to non-technical users</li>
        <li>🧠 Using <strong>Large Language Models</strong> (LLMs) in business intelligence</li>
        <li>🚚 Real-time analytics in <strong>logistics optimisation</strong></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>🤝 Let’s Connect</h2>
      <p>
        I'm always up for a conversation—whether it’s about data analytics, homelabs, automation, or a wild new tech idea. Feel free to <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/julianelliottdata" target="_blank">connect with me on LinkedIn</a> or drop me a message.
      </p>

      <blockquote>
        “In the age of information, ignorance is a choice.”
      </blockquote>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
